description: This week, our first place winner on the insightful side is an anonymous comment about Gina Carano’s lawsuit against Disney, in response to another commenter asserting that “all she’s asking for is consistency”: What makes you think she’s entitled to it? Disney is not bound by her subjective personal view of what she said. In […]
title: Funniest/Most Insightful Comments Of The Week At Techdirt
